@Database Changes_To_V1.03.guide

@Node Main "Changes to HydraBBS between V1.02 and V1.03"

  *** Sysop Information ***

  Please read *ALL* of this file, or you won't know about some of the great
  new features of this release.

  Go on, it'll only take you a couple of minutes.

  This document is stored as HBBS:Docs/Misc/Upgrades/Changes_To_V1.03.Guide


  Changes to HydraBBS between V1.02 and V1.03
  ===========================================

  * Control

    About text changed to fit on screens with a width of 640.

  * SysopListViewer

    Added the backfill, so now it looks right on screen with more than
    8 colours.

  * NewUserAnnouncer

    Created door, see the docs for installing and configuring it!
    @{"HBBS:Docs/Doors/NewUserAnnouncer.Guide" link HBBS:Docs/Doors/NewUserAnnouncer.Guide/MAIN}

  * MailAdd

    Fixed SERIOUS bug, an attempt was made to free memory incorrectly,
    causing a software failure or crash! (oops!)

    Fortunatly, none of the doors I had coded actually used this door in
    versions prior to V1.03. It's only when I created the NewUserAnnouncer
    door that I noticed this!

  * Mail General

    Fixed potential memory loss if a door accidently specified
    MailMsg->Data and a filename when calling PostMailMsg()

@EndNode
